    <p class="md:text-xl lg:text-3xl">WP&nbsp;Engine's new website should serve as the product demo for its own platform and for WordPress, showcasing integrations with 3rd party sales and marketing systems, extendability of the framework, robust content analytics, and ease-of-use for the humans who maintain it all.</p>
