    <h2>Profile builder form</h2>
    <p>The profile builder form is the first outward-facing component of our personalization engine. Users who complete the form are rewarded with customized content and messaging throughout the website. I worked with a developer to make it enticing and fun, and we are seeing user engagement. This initial version of the form will be improved over time.</p>

